    <font color="#FF0000"><i>[Quote from original post: Why arent there east
    coast/west coast servers?<br>
    <br>
    I live on the west coast, and on almost every weeknight raids of thigns like
    the planes begin around 3 or 4 PST, when the east coasters can play and Im
    at work.]</i><br>
